<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="Y" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Yoke-fellow" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Yoke-fellow,</orth> companion: <cit><quote>--s in arms,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 2.3.56" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 II, 3, 56</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>by his bloody side, y. to his honour-owing wounds, the noble Earl of Suffolk also lies,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 4.6.9" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 6, 9</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thou, his y. of equity,</quote> <bibl n="shak. lr 3.6.39" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. III, 6, 39</bibl></cit>.
